properties.name: Bora Bora
properties.description: This is the Four Seasons in Bora Bora. I have always wanted to go on vacation here but I think the resort is beautiful.

properties.name: Paris, France
properties.description: The next stop on my tour is the Eiffel Tower in Paris, France. I hope to visit it one day after I graduate college.

properties.name: Athens, Greece
properties.description: I have always wanted to visit Athens ever since I learned about its ancient history in many history classes. I also would love to go sight seeing and visit the beaches.

properties.name: Moscow, Russia
properties.description: The next place I would like to visit is Moscow, Russia because I am interested in the Russian culture and seeing the architecture of the buildings there.

properties.name: Honolulu, Hawaii
properties.description: The last place on my tour is Honolulu, Hawaii. I hope to vacation here in the near future because I heard it has very nice hotels and the people are extremely friendly.
